data.description:
"Discover this charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom oasis nestled on a sprawling 8.3-acre property. The home boasts a covered outbuilding and 2 car carport.

The kitchen is a highlight, featuring an inviting island and a cozy breakfast nook where you can enjoy your morning coffee. The den exudes warmth with its gas logs and a stunning rock fireplace, making it the perfect space for relaxation.

This home offers ample space, including an additional room that can serve as a game room, man cave, or even another bedroom. The master bedroom showcases an elegant trey ceiling, and the master bathroom pampers you with a garden tub and a separate shower.

Located in a tranquil and secluded setting, this property offers a retreat from the hustle and bustle of everyday life.
